Jaya(my cousin sister) and her hubby Purbayan visited us along withSatyajit on very rainy Sunday. They came to Paris for their own privateconcert. They were on a tour to Europe and playing Indian classicalmusic. Purbayan(sitar) and Satyajit (tabla) are very talented in theirown field.It was our great pleasure to have them as guest. Due to rainwe reached the concert bit late but it was a great performance. Anevening, which I will remember for a long time.A very bad week withMetro strike ended in delight.You can find lots of web sites&hellip;
